OL,3,CMet Police apologises to Stephen
OL,4,CLawrence's mother for 'broken promise'
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police Commissioner
OL,7,Fhas apologised to the mother of
OL,8,FStephen Lawrence for not fulfilling a
OL,9,Fpromise to answer questions stemming
OL,10,Ffrom a BBC investigation into the
OL,11,Fmurder of the 18-year-old.
OL,13,FThe broadcaster says Baroness Doreen
OL,14,FLawrence was promised an explanation
OL,15,Fafter the BBC last year named Matthew
OL,16,FWhite as the sixth suspect in the case.
OL,18,FDespite initial correspondence with
OL,19,FDeputy Assistant Commissioner Matt
OL,20,FWard, no update or explanation has
OL,21,Fbeen given.
