OL,3,CMet Police apologises to Stephen
OL,4,CLawrence's mother for 'broken promise'
OL,6,FCommissioner Sir Mark Rowley has now
OL,7,Fissued an apology, saying: "On top of
OL,8,Fthe failures over the decades this is
OL,9,Ftotally unacceptable."
OL,11,FMr Lawrence was murdered by a gang of
OL,12,Fracists in Eltham, south-east London,
OL,13,Fin April 1993, as he ran to catch a
OL,14,Fbus with his friend Duwayne Brooks.
OL,16,FOnly two of his killers ` Gary Dobson
OL,17,Fand David Norris ` have ever been
OL,18,Fbrought to justice.
