OL,3,CMet Police apologises to Stephen
OL,4,CLawrence's mother for 'broken promise'
OL,6,FThe original investigation into his
OL,7,Fdeath was hampered by institutional
OL,8,Fracism in the Metropolitan Police, and
OL,9,Fclaims that corrupt officers had
OL,10,Fsought to protect Norris, whose father
OL,11,FClifford Norris was a notorious drug
OL,12,Fdealer.
OL,14,FLast June, the BBC named White, who
OL,15,Fdied aged 50 in 2021, and outlined the
OL,16,Fbungled handling of the evidence
OL,17,Fagainst him.
