OL,3,CMet Police apologises to Stephen
OL,4,CLawrence's mother for 'broken promise'
OL,6,FTwo witnesses said White had confessed
OL,7,Fto being present during the attack,
OL,8,Fone of whom, his stepfather, was not
OL,9,Fspoken to by police until 20 years
OL,10,Fafter the murder because officers had
OL,11,Fpreviously misidentified him.
OL,13,FThe Met said White was arrested twice
OL,14,Fin connection with the murder, but on
OL,15,Fboth occasions there was not enough
OL,16,Fevidence for a prosecution.
OL,18,FBaroness Lawrence told the BBC:
OL,19,F"(White)'s probably the key one who
OL,20,Fprobably caused Stephen's murder, and
OL,21,F(the Met) did nothing about it.
