OL,3,CMet Police apologises to Stephen
OL,4,CLawrence's mother for 'broken promise'
OL,6,F"I'm not sure what they're hiding
OL,7,Fbehind, why they can't come and tell
OL,8,Fme exactly what they knew then."
OL,10,FSir Mark said: "We recognise this is a
OL,11,Fparticularly difficult time for the
OL,12,FLawrence family and Duwayne Brooks. I
OL,13,Fam sorry our failure to respond in a
OL,14,Ftimely fashion has added to this.
OL,16,F"On top of the failures over the
OL,17,Fdecades this is totally unacceptable.
