OL,6,F"Restoring trust in the Met is one of
OL,7,Fmy top priorities and that includes
OL,8,Fhow we work with those affected by the
OL,9,Ffailures of the past.
OL,11,F"I apologise to Baroness Lawrence who
OL,12,Fmust have answers to all her
OL,13,Fquestions. I have written to her and
OL,14,Foffered to meet."
